{"tid":2167346,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民檢測前 限聚拒放寬 變相強迫參與  議員斥為政治犧牲百業","createTime":"2020-08-21T05:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T05:08:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2d57f532880de0721ae09359bb99f000c6cce2dd","tid":2167346,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/4LHQSEMLKJAJPITEKDL2XHZ3VU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2F4LHQSEMLKJAJPITEKDL2XHZ3VU%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuxnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=75de5f3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2F4LHQSEMLKJAJPITEKDL2XHZ3VU%2F&h=39bce2a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/4LHQSEMLKJAJPITEKDL2XHZ3VU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民檢測前 限聚拒放寬 變相強迫參與 <br />\n議員斥為政治犧牲百業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：基層近半工時減 逾60%焦慮<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府推出的全民檢測將由9月1日開始，為期兩周。雖然現時疫情開始放緩，但政府已決定在全民檢測完成前，不會放寬社交距離限制措施，變相逼全港市民參與檢測。政府將於全港各區的社區會堂及學校禮堂設採樣中心，每日朝8至晚8收集市民的深喉及鼻腔樣本，估計需要8,400名醫護人員分三更參與協助採樣，但目前僅有2,000多人報名，距離目標甚遠。<br />\n<br />\n近日單日確診個案趨下降趨，市民也出現抗疫疲勞，盼一些社交距離措施鬆綁，尤其盼食肆恢復晚上堂食。但《南華早報》。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：民間推350元化驗防資料送中<br />\n<br />\n公民黨議員郭家麒批評，全民檢測要封關及全港禁足令配合才有實效，現由內地專家主導的全民檢測只是場「政治騷」。林鄭政府。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qtsqvOoQwVXaoLsHfL8Ezln3LQI=/1788x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YKRBPJGTDJDQVJXF4OFUZIC2XA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqtsqvOoQwVXaoLsHfL8Ezln3LQI%3D%2F1788x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYKRBPJGTDJDQVJXF4OFUZIC2XA.jpg&h=6bb81685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■康文署為配合防疫圍封轄下設施，消息指相關措施在全民檢測前難望解禁。 歐新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n18區設採樣中心助拭鼻咽<br />\n<br />\n全民檢測最快9月1日展開，據悉政府最快日內公佈詳情，包括18區設立採樣中心。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府較早前開始為全民檢測計劃招募醫護人員，協助招募的西醫工會會長楊超發。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n需招8,400醫護惟反應冷淡<br />\n<br />\n楊指協助採樣的醫護分三更當值，每更四小時。政府要求參與醫護每日最少參與兩更。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫學會主席蔡堅在電台節目亦稱，醫學會僅協助招募到百多名醫護參與，反。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前指負責檢測的人員只會獲得貼有編碼的試管，不知道市民的個人資料，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hApUorREUHaaWlCz_cyjOCvVeiA=/1774x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZOPCHQG5DVEAJHI4QWFYQPAVK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhApUorREUHaaWlCz_cyjOCvVeiA%3D%2F1774x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZOPCHQG5DVEAJHI4QWFYQPAVK4.jpg&h=10c94321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊超發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/h1QtGwCw-ydZ8w37Ydj2ZmYc_cw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ADDU3OULLZGDFGU7PYJN2JXYOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fh1QtGwCw-ydZ8w37Ydj2ZmYc_cw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FADDU3OULLZGDFGU7PYJN2JXYOM.jpg&h=a0c5db1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡 堅"}]}